Combine crust ingredients and mix well. Press firmly onto bottom and sides of 9-in. pan. Chill 30 minutes. For filling, combine cream cheese, eggs, brown sugar, buttermilk and vanilla in food processor. Process about 3 minutes or until smooth and free of lumps. Pour into crust, top with toasted almonds. Bake at 350 degrees F for about 30 minutes until lightly browned. Cool, then cover and refrigerate at least 3 hours. Serve chilled.